    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's like, if the end result is always going to be zero, then the struggle to stay alive just feels like extra, unnecessary work. people talk about \"making an impact\" or \"leaving a legacy\" like that actually matters in the grand scheme of things. it's just a way to distract ourselves from the fact that we're essentially nothing. if nothing matters, then why keep going through the motions?",
